---
import { cvtPath } from "../../lib/site";
import MapNode from "./MapNode.astro";
import { cvtPilotLabel } from "../../lib/cvt-narrative";
---

<section class="map-section" id="user-layer">
  <p class="map-kicker">1 · {cvtPilotLabel}</p>
  <h2 class="map-heading">What people see today</h2>
  <p class="map-lead">
    The transport pilot's public channels — starting with the simplest interaction: a plate on WhatsApp. The same pattern will extend to other service providers as new categories join the platform.
  </p>

  <div class="map-diagram mt-10">
    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <MapNode label="PUBLIC" variant="highlight" class="min-w-[8rem]" />
    </div>
    <div class="map-connector map-connector-down mx-auto h-8 w-px" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-6">
      <MapNode label="WhatsApp" sub="Lookup" href={cvtPath("#whats-live")} />
      <MapNode label="Passport" sub="& Profile" href={cvtPath("concepts/trust-passport")} />
      <MapNode label="Reports" sub="& Feedback" href={cvtPath("guides/moderation-framework")} />
    </div>
    <div class="map-connector map-connector-merge mx-auto mt-0 h-10 w-full max-w-md" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg class="h-full w-full" viewBox="0 0 400 40" preserveAspectRatio="none" fill="none">
        <path d="M67 0 V20 H200 M333 0 V20 H200 M200 20 V40" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <MapNode label="Good Standing" variant="hub" href={cvtPath("concepts/good-standing")} class="min-w-[10rem]" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <blockquote class="map-quote mt-10">
    The pilot proves the model on the road. The platform makes trust portable everywhere people work.
  </blockquote>

  <p class="mt-6">
    <a href={cvtPath("vision#transport-pilot")} class="btn-ghost !px-0 !text-sm">Read why transport is the first pilot →</a>
  </p>
</section>
